				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\eta = \frac{{V_{\text{mp}} \times J_{\text{mp}} }}{{P_{\text{in}} }} = \frac{{V_{\text{OC}} \times J_{\text{SC}} \times FF}}{{P_{\text{in}} }}$$\end{document}

Hence the fill factor can be calculated by Eq. 2:2FF=Vmp×JmpVOC×JSC\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
